Package skipiste.algorithm

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GraphNode
    Interface implemented by the Node class that guarantees methods required by the shortes path algorithms and the path builder are implemented.
    SearchAlgorithm
    Interface that all search algorithms must implement
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSearchAlgorithm<T extends GraphNode>
    AbstractSearchAlgorithm provides a Generic Abstract Superclass for Shortest Path algorithms and some basic functionality commonly shared.
    NodeDecorator
    An abstract decorator class that the algorithm specific classes will implement in order to add their extra functionality.
    Path
    Represents a the path calculated by the route planning algorithms.
